  "detailed_description": "<h1>Check this great games</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/270aa29132566caf990f1770ef36c29a.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>The story for “Boiling Steel” was written by one of the authors of <strong>S.T.A.L.K.E.R.</strong> series. <br><br>According to the plot you are one of many who set off in search of a better life in the distant bastion of scientific progress. Your goal is a colony planet, free from bureaucratic, religious and other radical restrictions. It is a high-tech paradise. But here, something went wrong…<br><br>Reach the final to know what’s happened.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/d276c74f59afc52d02d0497f0885390b.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>The action of the game takes place on a planet-colony in biomes, different in climatic and biological features and locations, unique in their content. <br><br>More than 40 combat missions, each of which unfolds on a unique map - from the cloud-city complexes and sandy mining platforms to the permafrost zone and science camps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/34becf923a298b0a53062f1d64eda2ab.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>11 different tools with the original mechanic of two-handed grip allow the player to choose their own playing style. <br>The stripping cutter (<i>like a lightsaber sword</i>) and the fisticuffs are also in your arsenal.<br>The weapon upgrade system automatically improves a favorite and frequently used tool, gradually turning it into a hellish machine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/d3b4ac9f0a672edc590cf299612fed87.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>A number of additional abilities increase your combat effectiveness. Among those:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>clone<br></li><li>superspeed<br></li><li>defense matrix<br></li><li>electromagnetic wave<br></li><li>plasma stripping system</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/270aa29132566caf990f1770ef36c29a.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>The story for “Boiling Steel” was written by one of the authors of <strong>S.T.A.L.K.E.R.</strong> series. <br><br>According to the plot you are one of many who set off in search of a better life in the distant bastion of scientific progress. Your goal is a colony planet, free from bureaucratic, religious and other radical restrictions. It is a high-tech paradise. But here, something went wrong…<br><br>Reach the final to know what’s happened.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/d276c74f59afc52d02d0497f0885390b.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>The action of the game takes place on a planet-colony in biomes, different in climatic and biological features and locations, unique in their content. <br><br>More than 40 combat missions, each of which unfolds on a unique map - from the cloud-city complexes and sandy mining platforms to the permafrost zone and science camps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/34becf923a298b0a53062f1d64eda2ab.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>11 different tools with the original mechanic of two-handed grip allow the player to choose their own playing style. <br>The stripping cutter (<i>like a lightsaber sword</i>) and the fisticuffs are also in your arsenal.<br>The weapon upgrade system automatically improves a favorite and frequently used tool, gradually turning it into a hellish machine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016860/extras/d3b4ac9f0a672edc590cf299612fed87.avif?t=1713947617\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>A number of additional abilities increase your combat effectiveness. Among those:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>clone<br></li><li>superspeed<br></li><li>defense matrix<br></li><li>electromagnetic wave<br></li><li>plasma stripping system</li></ul>",
